{"tid":1664146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國跨黨派議員去信庫克 要求讓HKmap.live恢復上架","createTime":"2019-10-20T01:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T02:46:13.000Z","uid":68738,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb46b88a9c318ba94ae52d85dff433595b55eb12","tid":1664146,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"香港互動地圖軟件「HKmap即時地圖」（HKmap.live）手機應用程式，被內地官媒抨擊後，遭蘋果App Store下架，美國民主共和兩黨議員特意去信蘋果，要求讓該程恢復上架。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）、魯比奧（Marco Rubio）、民主黨參議員懷登（Ron Wyden）和眾議員奧卡西奧科迪斯（Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez）等7名議員，跨黨派聯署去信蘋果行政總裁庫克（Tim Cook），要求讓「HKmap即時地圖」恢復上架，「你曾在公開場合指出你希望與中國的領袖合作，尋求改變，而非坐在一旁指罵他們，我們，同樣地，相信外交和貿易是推動民主化的力量，但當一個打壓人民的政府拒絕進化，或事實上，是每況愈下時，合作便等於合謀。」7名議員亦分別去信動視暴雪，要求對方收回早前公開禁止遊戲玩家發言支持香港社運的決定。<br />\n<br />\n「HKmap即時地圖」在蘋果App Store上架後，便被內地官媒大肆抨擊，結果被蘋果官方以「用於追蹤和伏擊警察，威脅公共安全」為由，數日內極速下架。但其Andriod版本的應用程式，自9月17日至今一直在Google Play Store上架，下載次數超過1萬，暫為熱門免費手機應用程式排行榜第2位，其間沒遭受官媒狙擊。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司於本月9日曾公開指，已就事件展開調查，又指曾收到多宗香港的顧客就該程式作出查詢，公司認為程式對執法者及市民有威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191019/60172248?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191019%2F60172248%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc%2FvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=c639369c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191019%2F60172248%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=42862603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191019/60172248?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5babaf5a2c68f85871e9b3cd3f3d9f1fad2be1f8","tid":1664146,"uid":280493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQEGUrP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQEGUrP.gif&h=1f9286ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"209bb782266d9dc8532b94d4f8435b4ba2c80333","tid":1664146,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當一個打壓人民的政府拒絕進化，或事實上，是每況愈下時，合作便等於合謀。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bddaf58d118fedb357be7e97be0e1aacda3087df","tid":1664146,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:28:21.000Z","msg":"（再開post）【手足請入】新戰術-分身術草船借箭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1664149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1664149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de7650414e8140f8dbe420e445f22fe582ff40ed","tid":1664146,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:29:01.000Z","msg":"美軍來了"},{"pid":"e7aa9295fa1c959f03c9e4d3cff00952613abef1","tid":1664146,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5713346a77b46201624a716661ae0a923364318","tid":1664146,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook 有排煩"},{"pid":"3807bb19314aa9fd13a4d2ad2eedda4067d70ab1","tid":1664146,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass